## What It Is
A step refinement process is a structured workflow for iterative improvement of system prompts. It defines a specific refinement path that can be executed repeatedly across different contexts. Step refinements are NOT agents (P02, which define identity/persona) nor system_prompts (P03, which define communication style). A steps answers "what phases execute to achieve this refinement?" while agents answer "who am I?" and prompts answer "how do I communicate?"

