## Key Parameters
| Parameter | Type | Default | Tradeoff |
|-----------|------|---------|----------|
| refinement_type | enum | "iterative" | iterative vs one-time refinement |
| phases | array | required | More phases = granular control vs complexity |
| input_schema | object | {} | Strong typing vs flexibility |
| output_format | string | "markdown" | Structured output vs natural language |
| timeout_seconds | int | 330 | Execution time limit vs complex workflows |

## Phase Structure
| Phase | Purpose | Input | Output |
|-------|---------|-------|--------|
| analyze | Context assessment | artifact, feedback | analysis_report |
| prioritize | Improvement focus | analysis_report | priority_matrix |
| execute | Refinement workflow | priority_matrix | refined_artifact |
| validate | Quality assurance | refined_artifact, criteria | validation_report |

## Refinement Patterns
| Pattern | Example | Activation |
|--------------|---------|------------|
| Iterative refinement | "Refine → Review → Repeat" | User initiates multiple cycles |
| One-time refinement | "Finalize → Archive" | Single pass refinement |
| Parallel refinement | "Multiple reviewers → Concurrent edits" | Simultaneous improvements |
| Sequential refinement | "Draft → Review → Finalize" | Step-by-step improvements |

